Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.98,sign_24_2_Thirteen,Sign 0000,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:07.69,sign_72_3_Tokyo_Internatio,Sign 0007,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo International Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:07.69,Main Dialogue,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,The first-years should be in the \Nmiddle of the second stage by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:10.69,Main Dialogue,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows if we'll actually participate,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:12.78,Main Dialogue,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,but it's always better to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:14.53,Main Dialogue,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Akanegakubo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:16.78,Main Dialogue,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,I hate planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:18.70,Main Dialogue,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.71,0:00:21.10,Main Dialogue,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a spoiled brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:21.76,Main Dialogue,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:23.54,Main Dialogue,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,No!
