Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:26.96,sign_606_14_Totsuki_Elite_Te,Sign 0026,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki Elite Ten \N{\fs26} Saito Somei
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:33.13,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,It's great to tour Hokkaido for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:34.84,sign_795_16_Totsuki_Elite_Te,Sign 0034,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki Elite Ten \N{\fs26} Kinokuni Nene
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.55,sign_836_17_Totsuki_Elite_Te,Sign 0035,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki Elite Ten \N{\fs26} Eizan Etsuya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:40.02,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsukasa, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.02,0:00:41.54,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,It looks really tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:44.31,Main Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,Rindo... Don't forget about the exams, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:46.02,sign_1063_21_Totsuki_Elite_Te,Sign 0045,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki Elite Ten \N{\fs26} Kobayashi Rindo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:50.02,sign_1161_22_Former_Totsuki_E,Sign 0049,0000,0000,0000,,Former Totsuki Elite Ten\N 7th Seat \N{\fs26} Isshiki Satoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:53.24,sign_1236_23_Former_Totsuki_E,Sign 0052,0000,0000,0000,,Former Totsuki Elite Ten\N 8th Seat \N{\fs26} Kuga Terunori
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:56.91,sign_1324_24_Former_Totsuki_E,Sign 0056,0000,0000,0000,,Former Totsuki Elite Ten\N 3rd Seat \N{\fs26} Megishima Tosuke
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:02.91,sign_1462_25_Totsuki_Elite_Te,Sign 0102,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki Elite Ten\N 1st Seat \N{\fs26} Tsukasa Eishi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:06.96,sign_1547_26_Totsuki_Elite_Te,Sign 0107,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki Elite Ten\N 10th Seat \N{\fs26} Nakiri Erina
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:37.61,sign_6424_110_Food_Wars,Sign 0107,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(654,1)}Food Wars
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:37.61,sign_1937_22_The_Third_Plate,Sign 0107,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(654,1)}The Third Plate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:37.61,sign_1975_23_Totsuki_Train_Ar,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1150,1)}Totsuki Train Arc
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:40.87,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The train might've stopped \Nin Sapporo Station,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:45.93,sign_3848_30_Jeanne_D_Arc_Ris,Sign 0241,0000,0000,0000,,Jeanne D'Arc Rises
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:43.38,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,but we totally went right \Nthrough the city itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:45.93,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad, given that it's \Na famous sightseeing spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.89,sign_3979_34_Totsuki_Academy_,Sign 0247,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki Academy Advancement Exams \N Stage Two Examination Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.89,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We got taken to the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:52.98,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing but mountains around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:55.61,Main Dialogue,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could've taken the \Ntime to walk around and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:56.98,Main Dialogue,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,like in Odori Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:02:58.74,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.65,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired after the long train trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:04.83,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,I am Endo, Totsuki lecturer and \Nyour examiner for the second stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:06.81,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,This stage will be an individual exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:08.75,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Also, instead of specifying \Nan ingredient to prepare,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:09.96,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,you are to make a noodle dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:11.01,Main Dialogue,Stu,0000,0000,0000,,Noodle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:11.92,Main Dialogue,Stu,0000,0000,0000,,...dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:15.29,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of noodles, Hokkaido is famous \Nfor having a wide variety of ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:20.15,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Sapporo ramen, Hakodate ramen, \NAsahikawa ramen, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:23.75,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,There are many restaurants renowned \Nfor their udon and soba, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:28.52,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Hokkaido is the top domestic producer \Nof buckwheat by far, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.95,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Given how vast the prefecture is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:33.09,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,it's not surprising that \NHokkaido gave rise to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:36.27,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,a diversity of noodle dishes that \Nreflect regional differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:39.28,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,With that in mind, let's try \Nmaking a noodle dish today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.69,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So we can make any noodle dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:44.74,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,When there are so many \Noptions, it's hard to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:49.50,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,But there are only basic ingredients here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.25,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:53.21,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,We have many different kinds of noddles here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:55.92,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,In addition to green onions \Nand other basic vegetables,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:59.63,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,we have already prepared basic \Ncomponents such as broth and stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:03.59,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,But those aren't enough to construct \Na gourmet dish, as you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:07.55,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll be tasked with sourcing \Nany missing ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:12.96,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,If you can present a single serving \Nof a noodle dish that can impress me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:13.99,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,you'll pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:16.15,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,You have three hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:18.71,Main Dialogue,Stu,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? We have to start \Nby getting ingredients?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:21.61,Main Dialogue,Stu,0000,0000,0000,,But if we get a taxi, we can get to an \Nurban area within thirty minutes or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:24.11,Main Dialogue,Stu,0000,0000,0000,,The central wholesale market's close, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:26.32,Main Dialogue,Stu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to get high-quality ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:30.79,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Enter the exam hall in the order in which \Nyour name is called and start cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:33.79,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama, this way to Hall A, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:34.57,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.96,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,The next three, off to Hall B!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:39.67,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Hall C!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.72,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:50.93,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We rebels are being left until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:51.93,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:56.18,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Ibusaki Shun, Marui Zenji, \NIsami Aldini—to Hall A!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:57.52,Main Dialogue,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we got called.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:04.24,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaki Ryoko, Arato Hisako, Nakiri \NAlice, Kurokiba Ryo—to Hall B!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:08.59,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino Yuki, Mito Ikumi, \NSato Shoji, Aoki Daigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:09.45,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,You're in Hall C!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:12.16,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,The remaining three of you, to Hall D!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.12,sign_7485_85_Hall_D,Sign 0513,0000,0000,0000,,Hall D
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:19.18,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Mister Examiner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:22.22,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're supposed \Nto make a noodle dish,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.63,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,there are no noodles left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.54,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:28.30,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,You are to source any \Ningredients you don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:31.26,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you need to do for this exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:32.06,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:35.81,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,There are barely any ingredients\N like flour or rice flour left
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.43,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,that might help us make noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:39.95,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:42.60,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,They won't even give us any ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:44.82,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,But what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.65,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sapporo is a major city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.45,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we can find a noodle factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:52.33,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,We can hand-make noodles by getting flour \Nand buckwheat flour and stuff, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.13,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:55.29,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll figure something \Nout in three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.26,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:59.00,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Now that that's settled, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:07.72,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't the only reason why you \Nweren't called until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.93,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.14,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to call a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:17.26,Italics Dialogue,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:19.21,Italics Dialogue,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,That mansion all the way up in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:21.82,Italics Dialogue,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, that's not possible right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.45,Italics Dialogue,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to wait for the \Nsnow plows to come through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:25.78,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.56,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,We have no way of getting out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:30.25,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,If we were in a novel or a movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:33.45,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,someone would definitely get\N killed right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.91,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:35.97,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:37.37,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious about walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.91,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to get lost in the mountains?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:42.21,sign_9565_120_Severe_Storm_in_,Sign 0640,0000,0000,0000,,Severe Storm in Sapporo Until Evening
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:42.21,Italics Dialogue Top,News,0000,0000,0000,,The snow that began falling around \Nnoon has quickly intensified
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:46.71,Italics Dialogue,News,0000,0000,0000,,into a major blizzard in the Sapporo \Nmountains rarely observed in recent years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:51.33,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,The other students have all passed the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:53.44,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,If we can fail those who remain,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:55.31,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,my job is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.98,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:01.09,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Glory to Central!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:01.69,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.40,sign_10111_129_Internal_Line_1,Sign 0703,0000,0000,0000,,Internal Line 1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.29,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:06.45,Italics Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Lecturer Endo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:08.45,Italics Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,The rebels are somehow, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:10.85,Italics Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Just please come now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.07,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:17.49,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Once you have enough for your\N own dish, send the ingredients over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:18.29,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:19.79,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,We need enough for Tadokoro-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:21.09,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:25.02,Italics Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,H-How are they starting \Nprep like nothing's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:27.00,Italics Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,There are no more noodles left!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.41,Italics Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Did they manage to get \Nnoodles in this blizzard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:31.17,Italics Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,No, impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.98,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at us \Nlike that, Mister Examiner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:38.22,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't honestly think you could stop \Nus with something like that, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:42.78,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we've been through \Ntraining a hundred times worse
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:45.47,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,than childish tricks like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.24,sign_11324_147_Help,Sign 0754,0000,0000,0000,,Help
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:05.78,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hang on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.25,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,We'll serve up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:10.92,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,the ultimate bowl of noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:22.94,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're working steadily, as though \Nthey already have noodles ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:25.90,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! It's just an act!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:30.47,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way they will pass \Nunder these circumstances!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:32.11,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,They're completely finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:34.46,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to my waiting room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:35.49,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Endo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.94,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:39.38,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Er, well, Hall C...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:43.35,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,And apparently Hall A and Hall B, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:44.71,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:49.29,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,All the rebels are finishing \Nup their noodle dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.05,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.68,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Examiner, if you wanted to fail us,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:58.05,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,you really shouldn't have\N left this lying around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:00.26,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Potatoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.60,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Home cooking from\N Hokkaido's Kutchan region...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.31,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:09.57,sign_13075_168_Kucchan_City,Sign 0908,0000,0000,0000,,Kutchan City
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:10.09,Italics Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Kutchan City is known for very heavy snowfall,\N even by Hokkaido's standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:12.03,Italics Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,They are a major producer of potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:15.99,Italics Dialogue,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,That's where the noodles \Nhighlighting the starch
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:19.20,Italics Dialogue,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,from the renowned variety, \NIrish Cobbler, was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:24.16,Italics Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,Potato starch comprises up \Nto 95 percent of the noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:22.41,sign_13457_174_Potato__Starch__,Sign 0922,0000,0000,0000,,Potato\N Starch\N 95%
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:22.41,sign_13457_175_Other_5_,Sign 0922,0000,0000,0000,,Other\N5%
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:24.83,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:26.54,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's gosetsu udon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:30.46,Italics Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,First, steam Irish Cobbler \Npotatoes and remove the skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:33.63,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Make them into fluffy mashed potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:37.34,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Then add water, salt, and flour,\N and knead into a dough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:40.89,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't enough wheat flour, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:44.18,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,but potato starch can be a substitute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:44.18,sign_13954_183_Missing,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato Starch
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.98,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,The potato starch that was to be used \Nto flour the noodle prep surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:49.15,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Potatoes are the base ingredient, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.93,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's not typically used in noodles,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:54.36,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,but it's a different story \Nwhen it comes to gosetsu udon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:57.83,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It works great as a binding agent,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:10:01.33,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,and makes a great starchy, elastic dough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.53,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:05.25,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,But so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:08.50,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,If you think you can just plop some \Ngreen onions on that and call it a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.00,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:14.74,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,The others all sourced high-quality \Ningredients before the blizzard hit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:19.01,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,and created dishes worthy of \Nbeing called gourmet food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:23.22,Flashback Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:27.17,Flashback Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Potatoes are an extremely \Nversatile ingredient!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:32.37,Flashback Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,If you can understand and leverage \Ntheir unique characteristics,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:34.44,Flashback Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,they will help you in a time of need!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:38.15,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can use {\i0}that{\i1} as the topping...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:39.45,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.91,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,There are other tasks left to do\N after making the noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.42,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:45.66,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.29,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:57.55,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The Hokkaido Seminar Special Gosetsu Udon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:58.97,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.57,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:03.02,Italics Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the only ingredients left \Nthey could've used as toppings
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:05.64,Italics Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,were green onions and perilla leaves, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.10,Italics Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:09.68,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please eat before \Nthe noodles get soggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:11.06,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:24.82,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this mellow broth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:27.22,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,It's been thickened just \Nenough to coat the noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:29.33,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,What broad umami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:32.12,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I added grated potatoes to the broth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.79,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's how the broth got \Nthickened in a good way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:38.76,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, potatoes have \Na lot of glutamic acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:43.22,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That umami compound has \Nspread throughout the broth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.19,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The potatoes were coarsely grated,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:49.98,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,so the tiny potato bits throughout \Nthe broth provide texture, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.94,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,And what about the critical topping?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:01.38,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,It's potato mochi, a popular souvenir\N for Hokkaido's visitors to take home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:04.57,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Light and chewy,\N it's crispy on the outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:07.11,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Complimented by the thick soup,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:11.79,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,it contrasts with the slippery noodles \Nand heightens the diner's satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:13.62,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:18.34,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,The full range of the potato's \Ncharacteristics are crammed into this bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.61,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.01,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Irish Cobbler's—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:24.66,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Irish Cobbler's starch, texture, \Nand umami concentrated into one dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:27.00,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,In a nutshell, it's the \Nultimate potato noodle dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.18,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.18,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Please score the dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:29.89,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:37.94,Italics Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,These are impressive variations \Non the gosetsu udon, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:40.28,Italics Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,How did they manage to \Ncreate these on the fly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:43.24,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Mister Examiner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:50.09,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira Soma, Takumi Aldini, \Nand Tadokoro Megumi—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:52.66,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You all pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:54.87,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Glad you enjoyed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:56.83,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:58.79,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:01.25,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,You all pass, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.38,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Erinacchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.41,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:07.97,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to your Hokkaido Seminar, we passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:12.57,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to do it all \Non my own, thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:13.81,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:16.27,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,I see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:19.50,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,If only you had not interfered, Erina-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:23.61,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,scum like this would've been easily eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:26.51,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,They only survived thanks to your mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:28.84,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,If only you had not put \Nideas into their head...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:29.95,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,You are wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:35.31,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I only taught them about the unique \Ncharacteristics of potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:38.57,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones who thought of how to \Nbuild on gosetsu udon as the main concept
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:40.00,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,and highlight the strength of potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:43.06,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Heed my warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:47.51,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,These chefs are far beyond the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.51,Italics Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:52.85,Italics Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,How could the rebels have \Nbanded together like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:55.98,Italics Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Such is Erina-sama's \Nawe-inspiring leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:56.77,Italics Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,It's as though...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:14:00.15,Italics Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,It's as though she is Jeanne d'Arc, \Nthe saintly female knight commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:04.07,Italics Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,trying take back Totsuki \Nfrom Central's rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:07.49,Main Dialogue,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:10.65,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:13.91,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,All the rebels have passed stage two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:17.37,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we will send for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.11,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:25.77,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sapporo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:26.20,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Major city!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:27.01,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping district!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:32.53,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad they're letting us sightsee \Nthe city before the train leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:33.49,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:34.96,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,The train won't leave till the evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:36.14,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,so we have a good bit of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:38.92,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's eat something good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:39.49,Main Dialogue,Aooki,0000,0000,0000,,Ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:40.20,Main Dialogue,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,Sushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.10,Main Dialogue,Ibu,0000,0000,0000,,Genghis Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.57,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:48.28,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, think of this as part \Nof the Hokkaido Seminar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:52.53,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,There's no better lesson \Nthan to taste local dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.99,Main Dialogue,3,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, Erina-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:00.89,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,What is this rich flavor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.89,0:15:02.30,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the right amount of sweetness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.81,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,Pure, yet rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:05.26,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's too rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:08.96,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of milk are they using to \Nmake such good soft serve ice cream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:10.38,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hokkaido is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:13.35,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we'll just have to try everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:14.42,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:17.06,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,We must carefully discern \Nwhat is worth trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:19.38,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, Tanukikoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:21.17,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try going all the way to Susukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:24.02,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The diner duo's going full throttle, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.30,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going with your bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:29.90,Main Dialogue,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to walk around \Nthe Odori Park area, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:34.29,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,There's supposed to be a famous processed \Nseafood store in front of Sapporo Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:35.66,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come with, Arato-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.31,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:37.98,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,They have dried goods, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:39.54,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,like for your medicinal cuisine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:42.67,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:44.81,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, Hisako.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:45.79,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:49.26,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,You have the right to do what you want, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:52.47,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama... Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.77,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Nakiri-san, let's walk around here, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:56.85,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:16:02.98,sign_22942_314_Loyalty,Sign 1559,0000,0000,0000,,Loyalty
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:16:00.28,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you'll keep her safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:02.06,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Erina-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:02.98,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:10.35,Main Dialogue,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this a group you don't see often.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:13.57,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's an event going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.88,Main Dialogue,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there will be anything good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.88,0:16:18.41,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,E-Er, Erina-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:20.41,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like anything to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:22.02,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,I can go get something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.17,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, Mito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:26.13,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:34.92,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I've been to Sapporo many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:38.06,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,but this is the first time I've had \Nany time to take the sights in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:38.97,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:41.30,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,As the one possessing the God Tongue,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.85,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I've spent my days serving as a taster,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:45.65,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,meeting all the heavyweights \Nin the food industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:51.36,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It was almost always for those reasons \Nthat I would leave my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:54.32,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Looking back now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:57.47,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I may not have been trying to \Nsee anything out in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:02.50,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I was struggling to fulfill my \Nresponsibilities as the Nakiri family's heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.22,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:10.38,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,You were always amazing, Erina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:14.13,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,As a scion of the Mito family,\N I saw you on several occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:20.10,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,I think I understand the \Nhardships you've endured.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.42,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Mito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:22.39,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:25.02,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,My family and yours are worlds apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.61,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,and I know it's presumptive of me to think
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:30.07,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,that you and I were in a \Nremotely similar situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:33.90,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,But I was bound by my house, too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:39.27,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you must have felt \Nso much more pressure than I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:41.08,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,you always had a commanding presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:47.15,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,So, I... um, really respect you, Erina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:49.29,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:52.58,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to check out \Nwhat's going on over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:54.17,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Erina-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:57.80,Main Dialogue,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you sure you'll be all \Nright by yourself, Mito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:05.29,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you were able to \Npatch things up with Mito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:08.69,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,We were never really at odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:14.06,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I just cut her off after \Nshe lost that Shokugeki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:18.15,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,And yet... I didn't know she \Nthought of me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:21.11,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Tadokoro-san, thank you for the \Nroasted brown rice green tea, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:24.02,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't need to thank me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:26.82,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know if there's anything \NI can do to help, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:29.25,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,If you have other manga you want \Nto read, I can lend them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:30.13,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:34.13,sign_26620_363_With_Heart,Sign 1833,0000,0000,0000,,With Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:32.58,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,That manga was yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:34.13,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:37.48,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hisako and Yukihira-kun \Nwouldn't say whose they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:41.22,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's also my fault \Nfor not really asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:44.03,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I haven't returned them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:46.07,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:49.98,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I like something you like, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:53.82,Main Dialogue,TS,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:56.49,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Soma-kun, Takumi-kun! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:59.57,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we found a totally awesome-looking place,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:02.27,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,but there's way too much \Nwe want on their menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:03.84,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,You two haven't eaten dinner yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:06.00,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:08.83,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's order a ton and share \Neverything between the four of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.05,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:10.78,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:12.29,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Now that that's settled, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:14.49,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Nakiri. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.49,0:19:15.75,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:23.39,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I really wasn't trying to \Nsee anything at all before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:27.74,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know this city was so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:35.02,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:37.76,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the other guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:40.03,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they already got on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.61,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time to leave, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:44.22,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:45.16,sign_28372_389_Hisako,Sign 1944,0000,0000,0000,,Hisako
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:45.16,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.10,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.97,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:51.97,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hisako, what's wrong? Why are you so anxious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:55.60,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's because I don't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:57.62,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to board.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:59.22,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:19:59.84,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:01.72,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.80,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,The train left 30 minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:05.51,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:09.35,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,What's there to be so surprised about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:12.27,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,You knew how things would \Ngo from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.46,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Rindo-senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:16.48,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's really cold, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:22.83,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:26.45,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,The pamphlet mentioned that the \Ntrain route will diverge, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:31.20,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,In the worst case, you'll only see the \Nothers at the final stage of the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:34.79,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,And that's if you all make it to that stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:38.53,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,In the third-stage exam \Nthat's coming up next,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:42.01,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,all the rebels will be going \Nup against the Elite Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:50.07,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make this a fun trip.\N Right, Yukihira Soma?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:34.45,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up super early just thinking \Nabout how we'll face the Elite Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:35.81,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:38.25,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Tadokoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:41.38,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you were too nervous \Nto sleep long, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:44.21,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:47.03,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.03,0:22:50.27,Main Dialogue,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're like a kid looking forward \Nto a day at a theme park!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:52.55,Main Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:52.55,sign_32838_418_Under_Eye_Circle,Sign 2251,0000,0000,0000,,Under-Eye Circles
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.27,0:22:52.55,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're excited, too, Takumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:22:58.74,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I confirmed this later by phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.74,0:23:02.31,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,but we, the rebels, were split \Ninto four different routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:03.73,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.73,0:23:05.28,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I hope everyone's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:06.90,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:08.86,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:11.24,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't had breakfast yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.57,0:23:13.98,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,Come eat with me, since you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.98,0:23:14.91,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.91,0:23:16.57,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Tadokoro-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.57,0:23:17.44,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,Eat, eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.44,0:23:18.61,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,It's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:22.51,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, can you tell us \Nwhat the next exam will be about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:26.14,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,The exam topic for the rebels—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.14,0:23:28.71,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I would hope it involves \Na fair and just match.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.49,0:23:32.37,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,There'd better not be any of the \Ncowardly tactics we've endured so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:37.57,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah. That was all \Nwhat the examiners chose to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.57,0:23:40.27,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,We don't play dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:43.65,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So who am I gonna face?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:45.27,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be you, Rindo-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:49.03,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,No, your opponent's already right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:49.82,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:58.71,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,The newest member of the Elite Ten—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.95,0:24:02.73,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:05.92,sign_30623_420_Totsuki,,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:10.92,sign_34668_446_Food_Wars,,0000,0000,0000,,Food Wars
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:10.92,sign_34668_447_The_Third_Plate,,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Plate
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:10.92,sign_34668_445_Next_Episode___R,Sign 2407,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode   {\fs16}Revenge Match
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:10.92,Main Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we got through the tunnel,\Nthere was a snowy mountain.
